1 Be it enacted by the People of the State of Maine as follows:
2 Sec. 1. 20-A MRSA §1905 is enacted to read:
3 §1905. Withdrawal
4 The residents of a participating municipality of a municipal school unit within a school
5 union may petition and vote to withdraw from the school union in the same manner as a
6 single municipality within a school administrative unit may petition to withdraw from a
7 regional school unit in accordance with section 1466.
8 SUMMARY
99 This bill allows the residents of a participating municipality of a school administrative
